title: The Green Children of Woolpit
description: For Halloween, Sawbones is bringing you a story rooted in folklore and mystery: two children  showed up one day in the English town of Woolpit, speaking a strange language . . .and with green skin. But their curious appearance may have a logical and medical explanation, and we bring you our best guesses.
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin & Dr. Sydnee McElroy)
